{"id": 841, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中的你要直面哪些虚伪？", "description": "全是套路，全是套路！！", "record_count": 6276, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181345m6lv9L8D4PUx0NVG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-29T11:36:01Z", "options": [{"id": 55298, "content": "这次我也没考好啦…（结果考了前三名…）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500062}, {"id": 54533, "content": "“我是对事不对人”。。。其实就是看你不顺眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261864}, {"id": 61957, "content": "没事的时候人影都没见有事找我的时候一口一个亲爱的我听着都不舒服跟你很熟吗？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536541}, {"id": 54534, "content": "我就简单的说两句！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496145}, {"id": 61958, "content": "跟你说和秘密……别人的秘密", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536541}, {"id": 54535, "content": "哎，做自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258013}, {"id": 54536, "content": "有空常联系 ，一般都没有联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448126}, {"id": 54537, "content": "那，做人，就是要开心咯！这句话特别安慰人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461181}, {"id": 54793, "content": "我来出，没事，我来出。。。。。。。好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443036}, {"id": 54538, "content": "这都是为你好…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487724}, {"id": 62218, "content": "你挺好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538219}, {"id": 54539, "content": "我喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293223}, {"id": 54540, "content": "出来晒晒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496223}, {"id": 54541, "content": "要不是看你长得丑，我早就抽你了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494492}, {"id": 54543, "content": "我现在给不想谈恋爱和你是个好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496307}, {"id": 56591, "content": "矮矬穷 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486219}, {"id": 54544, "content": "“哎，都怪我太丑”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423847}, {"id": 54547, "content": "不好意思的哇!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458114}, {"id": 54548, "content": "我只是提一下哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468544}, {"id": 54550, "content": "“有时间一起出来玩啊”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456618}, {"id": 54551, "content": "A:你觉得我穿这件怎么样？B:还行，挺好看的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48265}, {"id": 54809, "content": "“我都没复习”“我玩了一天”“我都没准备”“我绩点很低”“我在图书馆浪了一天”“我最差的就是英语”“我论文也没写完”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319909}, {"id": 54554, "content": "虚伪？只剩下安静地直面了吧、", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496362}, {"id": 54555, "content": "我是为你好，相信我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236395}, {"id": 54556, "content": "分出前:同学:我这次班排肯定进步了前十五了     【哭】\n分出后:我:卧槽？！她班级前十【微笑】我尼玛才二十五往后？！\n同学:哎呀没事儿，下次加油就好了。我也只是xxx科给提了点分儿。我也没想到啊～", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004901OlDaqkNXS5Pun6tQ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496363}, {"id": 54557, "content": "“你是个好人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493291}, {"id": 54558, "content": "分出前:同学:我这次班排肯定进步了前十五了     【哭】\n分出后:我:卧槽？！她班级前十【微笑】我尼玛才二十五往后？！\n同学:哎呀没事儿，下次加油就好了。我也只是xxx科给提了点分儿。我也没想到啊～", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182638cRpG2xdKu5NUXJQo.jpg", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496363}, {"id": 58654, "content": "瘦子总在胖子嘴边闹嚷自己胖\n", "image": null, "praise_coun